Vegetation indices such as NDVI (Rouse et al. 1974) and enhanced vegetation index (EVI; Huete et al. 2002) mainly use reflectance at red (R) and near infra-red (NIR). For example, NDVI is calculated as follows:17NDVI=ρNIR-ρRρNIR+ρR\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
